                "key": "Finale sublime",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Quando usa un'</span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">abilità elementale</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">, il personaggio riceve un aumento dell'</span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">ATT</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> pari a un </span><span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">12%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">15%/18%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">21%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: #37FFFF\">24%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> per</span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\"> 15 s</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> e un </span><span style=\"color: #CCBFAD\">Legame vitale</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> pari a un 25% dei </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">PS max</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">. Quest'effetto può attivarsi una volta ogni </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">10 s</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">. Quando il </span><span style=\"color: #CCBFAD\">Legame vitale</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> si dissolve, è possibile ottenere fino a un massimo di </span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">150</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">187.5</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">225</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">262.5</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">300</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> di ATT, in base a un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">2.4%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">3%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">3.6%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">4.2%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">/</span><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">4.8%</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> della quantità totale del </span><span style=\"color: #CCBFAD\">Legame vitale</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> dissolto, per </span><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">15 s</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p>"
